verse = \lyricmode {
  They per -- se -- cute those wound -- ed by your hand,
and talk of those whose pains and sor -- rows please them.
Charge them with crime on crime; do not re -- lease them,
nor let them freed from guilt be -- fore you stand.
LORD, from the book of life blot out their names;
let none of them be in your scroll re -- cord -- ed.
Do not in -- clude them with those free from blame;
let good and e -- vil just -- ly be re -- ward -- ed.
